description:
&lt;p&gt;Dudley Group of Hospitals are looking for 6 experienced Band 2 Phlebotomists to support the on-going Covid-19 testing programme to help ensure we can provide the safest care for both our staff and patients moving forward and help to manage the Covid-19 disease across the Trust and community. This role will be on a six month fixed term basis initially.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will require you to travel within the community providing tests to both patients and staff. You will be expected to work across a seven day rota, however there will be no night shifts but long days may be required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be fully supported in the role and will be issued with the necessary PPE to carry out the role safely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ROLES &amp; RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of the Covid hub, you will be required to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Meet and greet patients and staff that require testing, ensuring you have checked their personal details against the information provided and adhered to all trust data protection policies and procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using the safety equipment and PPE provided ensure all tests are carried out effectively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure all equipment is set up and ready for the day ahead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make sure test are appropriately sealed and labelled sending them in accordance with Trust guidance in a timely manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Follow all infection control protocols ensuring the safety of yourself, colleagues and patients at all times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure you have the necessary equipment, information and PPE required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain contact with your base supervisor informing them of delays or issues as they arise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jessica Kennedy - Assistant Directorate Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact Details - jessica.kennedy7@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
